article.description: San Diego State 86, UC San Diego 51
article.headline: San Diego State 86, UC San Diego 51
article.linkText: San Diego State 86, UC San Diego 51
article.story: SAN DIEGO (AP) -- Robby Peters made 4-of-6 3-pointers Monday night to lead UC San Diego to a 59-56 win over Chapman. Peters, a sophomore, scored 14 points for the Titans (2-2) and freshman Clint Allard contributed 13 points and fellow frosh Andrew Hatch scored 11. Patrick Carney scored 20 points for the Panthers (2-2), with Zach Wheatley scoring 10 points and grabbing six rebounds. Chapman shot 39 percent from the floor, but converted 16-of-22 free throws. UC San Diego shot 46 percent and made 5-of-10 3-point shots.
